This module defines the tag {tablify}.<p>

{tablify} generates tables from, for example, tab separated fields in
newline separated records (this is the default).<p>

<p><b>Arguments:</b>
<pre>
 help                Display this text.
 cellseparator=str   Use str as the column-separator.
 rowseparator=str    Use str as the row-separator.
 cellalign=left|right|center
                     Align the contents of the cells.
 rowalign=left|right|center
                     Align the contents of the rows.
 nice                Generate ``nice'' tables. The first row is the title row. There are several additional
                     arguments available for nice.

   bgcolor,titlebgcolor,titlecolor,fgcolor0,fgcolor1
                     Color definitions.
   modulo            Sets the number of rows using the same color in a row
   {fields}<i>[num|text, ...]</i>{/fields}
                     Optional. This container tag sets the field type for each column. Numerical fields
                     will be right aligned and formated.
 
</pre>
